# pages-seo · environment variables
#
# IMPORTANT FOR THE 1-CLICK DEPLOY FLOW:
# Cloudflare's "Deploy to Cloudflare" button scans this file and
# prompts the user to fill in every key it finds. To keep that flow
# friction-free, ALL keys below are OPTIONAL — leave them blank in
# the deploy UI and pages-seo will auto-generate or auto-detect
# everything it needs on first run.
#
# You can still set any of these as Pages secrets later via:
#   wrangler pages secret put <KEY> --project-name=<slug>
#
# Local development: copy this to .env or .dev.vars and fill in.
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Site identity (optional — auto-detected from the request host)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# pages-seo reads the live host from the incoming request and writes
# friendly defaults into D1 on first run. Leave blank unless you
# want to force a specific brand label or canonical URL.
#
# SITE_NAME=My Site
# SITE_URL=https://example.com
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Security tokens (optional — auto-generated on first run)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# /api/setup generates these as 64-char random hex on the very first
# admin login and stores them in D1. You only need to set them here
# if you want to pin a specific value (e.g. for CI testing) or
# rotate an existing install's tokens.
#
# ADMIN_TOKEN=
# INDEXNOW_KEY=
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI providers (optional — Workers AI is the free default)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Workers AI runs out of the box, no key needed (uses the env.AI
# binding). Add any of the keys below to enable fallback providers
# — they're tried in registry order, so the first key you set wins
# when Workers AI is unavailable.
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GROQ_API_KEY=
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=
# TOGETHER_API_KEY=
# CEREBRAS_API_KEY=
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CTA / link overrides (optional)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Surface a call-to-action across rendered pages. All optional;
# defaults come from /admin → Settings.
#
# SITE_CTA=Sign up to get started.
# SITE_SIGNUP_URL=/signup
# SITE_LOGIN_URL=/login
# SITE_PRICING_URL=/pricing
# SITE_CONTACT_URL=/contact
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Model overrides (optional)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Each provider ships with a sensible default model. Override only
# if you have a strong opinion.
#
# WORKERS_AI_TEXT_MODEL=@cf/meta/llama-3.3-70b-instruct-fp8-fast
# WORKERS_AI_IMAGE_MODEL=@cf/black-forest-labs/flux-1-schnell
# OPENAI_TEXT_MODEL=gpt-5
# OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL=gpt-image-1
# ANTHROPIC_TEXT_MODEL=claude-opus-4-7
# GEMINI_TEXT_MODEL=gemini-2.5-pro
# GEMINI_IMAGE_MODEL=imagen-4.0-generate-001
# GROQ_TEXT_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile
# DEEPSEEK_TEXT_MODEL=deepseek-chat
# MISTRAL_TEXT_MODEL=mistral-large-latest
# TOGETHER_TEXT_MODEL=meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-Turbo
# CEREBRAS_TEXT_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b
